Description: Functions for detecting and analyzing rare events in data.
    Includes isolation forest and DBSCAN clustering for time series residuals.
    Handles time series with STL/LOESS, Fourier smoothing, and estimates 
    seasonality shifts. Also provides tools for spatial point matching, 
    and statistical testing for rare event patterns.
